sql_statement.static: SELECT Iteration, Phase, Port.Name AS PortName, Port.Location AS Location, L2tp.L2tpNodeType AS NodeType,  Sessions, SessionsUp, ConnectedSuccessCount, FailedConnectCount, MinSetupTime, MaxSetupTime, AvgSetupTime, AvgSuccessTransactionCount, Cfg.ConnectRate AS ConfigSetupRate, SuccSetupRate, NULL AS Verdict FROM PppoePortResults AS Res JOIN PppoxPortConfig AS Cfg ON Res.ParentHnd=Cfg.Handle JOIN Port AS Port ON  Cfg.ParentHnd=Port.Handle JOIN L2tpPortConfig AS L2tp ON L2tp.ParentHnd=Port.Handle, PppL2tp_Iter AS Iter

SELECT Iteration, Phase, Port.Name AS PortName, Port.Location AS Location, L2tp.L2tpNodeType AS NodeType, CASE WHEN TestMode='Tunnel' THEN CurrVal ELSE TunnelPerNode END * (LacCount +  LnsCount) AS TunnelCount, TunnelUpCount, TunnelDownCount, SessionUpCount, SessionDownCount, MinTunnelSetupTime, MaxTunnelSetupTime, AvgTunnelSetupTime, TunnelSetupRate, MinSessionSetupTime, MaxSessionSetupTime, AvgSessionSetupTime, SessionSetupRate, Cfg.TunnelConnectRate AS ConfigSetupRate, NULL AS Verdict FROM L2tpPortResults AS Res JOIN L2tpPortConfig AS Cfg ON  Res.ParentHnd=Cfg.Handle JOIN Port AS Port ON Port.Handle=Cfg.ParentHnd JOIN L2tpPortConfig AS L2tp ON Port.Handle=L2tp.ParentHnd, PppL2tp_Iter AS Iter, PppL2tp_Cfg AS Test
UPDATE PppL2tp_PppSessionResults SET Verdict=(SELECT PrevIterVerdict FROM PppL2tp_Iter) WHERE Iteration=(SELECT Iteration FROM PppL2tp_Iter)-1
UPDATE  PppL2tp_L2tpv2SessionResults SET Verdict=(SELECT PrevIterVerdict FROM PppL2tp_Iter) WHERE Iteration=(SELECT Iteration FROM PppL2tp_Iter)-1

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS PppL2tp_TrafficResults (Iteration INTEGER, PortName TEXT, PortHandle INTEGER, GeneratorSigFrameCount INTEGER, AnalyzerSigFrameCount INTEGER, AnalyzerDroppedCount INTEGER)

SELECT (SELECT Iteration FROM spirent_methodology_benchmarkstabilityiteratorcommand) AS 'Iteration', p.Name AS 'PortName', p.Handle AS 'PortHandle', gen.GeneratorSigFrameCount, ana.SigFrameCount AS 'AnalyzerSigFrameCount', ana.DroppedFrameCount AS 'AnalyzerDroppedCount' FROM GeneratorPortResults AS gen JOIN AnalyzerPortResults AS ana JOIN Port AS p WHERE gen.ParentPort == p.Handle AND ana.ParentPort == p.Handle

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS PppL2tp_TrafficResults_Failures (Iteration INTEGER, PortName TEXT, PortHandle INTEGER, GeneratorSigFrameCount INTEGER, AnalyzerSigFrameCount INTEGER, AnalyzerDroppedCount INTEGER)

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: PPP sessions failed to come up.
report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: All PPP sessions have come up.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE COUNT(*) WHEN 0 THEN 1  ELSE 0 END FROM sqlite_master WHERE type='table' AND  name='PppL2tp_PppIter_CFail'

sql_statement.static: SELECT Res.Iteration, Res.Phase, Sessions AS 'Session Count', SessionsUp AS 'Session Up Count', ConnectedSuccessCount AS 'Success Connect Count', FailedConnectCount AS 'Failed Connect Count', ConfigSetupRate AS 'Configured Setup Rate (sessions/s)', SuccSetupRate AS 'Successful Setup Rate (sessions/s)' FROM PppL2tp_PppSessionResults AS Res JOIN PppL2tp_Iter AS Iter ON Res.Iteration=Iter.Iteration, PppL2tp_Cfg AS Cfg WHERE  NodeType='LAC' AND (ConnectedSuccessCount!=Sessions OR FailedConnectCount>0)
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS PppL2tp_PppIter_RFail
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS PppL2tp_L2tpIter_CFail

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: L2TP tunnels failed to come up.
report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: All L2TP tunnels have come up.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE COUNT(*) WHEN 0 THEN 1  ELSE 0 END FROM sqlite_master WHERE type='table' AND  name='PppL2tp_L2tpIter_CFail'

sql_statement.static: SELECT Res.Iteration, Res.Phase, TunnelCount AS 'Tunnel Count',  TunnelUpCount AS 'Tunnel Up Count', TunnelDownCount AS 'Tunnel Down Count', ConfigSetupRate AS 'Configured Setup Rate (sessions/s)', TunnelSetupRate AS 'Tunnel Setup Rate (sessions/s)' FROM  PppL2tp_L2tpv2SessionResults AS Res JOIN PppL2tp_Iter AS Iter ON  Res.Iteration=Iter.Iteration, PppL2tp_Cfg AS Cfg WHERE NodeType='LAC' AND (TunnelUpCount!=TunnelCount OR TunnelDownCount>0)

report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: Tx/Rx Sig Frame Counts were greater than 0 and no packet loss.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT name FROM sqlite_master WHERE name='val_Iteration_Traffic_Results')) > 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Detected 0 Tx and/or Rx Sig Frames or packet loss was detected.

sql_statement.static: SELECT Iteration, PortName AS 'Port Name', GeneratorSigFrameCount AS 'Tx Sig Frame Count',  AnalyzerSigFrameCount AS 'Rx Sig Frame Count', AnalyzerDroppedCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count' FROM  PppL2tp_TrafficResults WHERE GeneratorSigFrameCount == 0 OR AnalyzerSigFrameCount == 0 OR AnalyzerDroppedCount > 0

SELECT Iteration, PortName, PortHandle, GeneratorSigFrameCount, AnalyzerSigFrameCount, AnalyzerDroppedCount FROM PppL2tp_TrafficResults WHERE GeneratorSigFrameCount == 0 OR AnalyzerSigFrameCount == 0 OR AnalyzerDroppedCount > 0
SELECT Beg.Iteration, Beg.Phase AS 'Test Phase', SUM(Sessions) AS 'Total Expected Session Count',
SUM(ConnectedSuccessCount) AS 'Total Success Connect Count',
SUM(DisconnectedSuccessCount) AS 'Total Success Disconnect Count',
SUM(FailedConnectCount) AS 'Total Failed Connect Count',
SUM(FailedDisconnectCount) AS 'Total Failed Disconnect Count',
SUM(ConfigSetupRate) AS 'Total Configured Connect Rate (sessions/s)',
SUM(SuccSetupRate) AS 'Total Successful Setup Rate (sessions/s)' FROM PppL2tp_PppSessionResults AS Beg
JOIN PppL2tp_PppSessionEndResults AS END ON Beg.Iteration=End.Iteration AND Beg.Location=End.Location
JOIN  PppL2tp_Iter AS Iter ON Beg.Iteration=Iter.Iteration
WHERE  Beg.NodeType='LAC'
SELECT Res.Iteration, Res.Phase AS 'Test Phase', SUM(TunnelCount) AS 'Total Expected Tunnel Count',
SUM(TunnelUpCount) AS 'Total Tunnels Up Count', SUM(TunnelDownCount) 'Total Tunnels Down Count',
SUM(ConfigSetupRate) AS 'Total Configured Tunnel Setup Rate',
SUM(TunnelSetupRate) AS 'Total Tunnel Setup Rate'
FROM PppL2tp_L2tpv2SessionResults AS Res JOIN PppL2tp_Iter AS Iter ON Res.Iteration=Iter.Iteration WHERE  NodeType='LAC'
SELECT Beg.PortName AS 'Port Name', Beg.Location,
CASE WHEN Beg.NodeType='LAC' THEN 'Client' ELSE 'Server' END AS 'Emulation Mode',
Sessions AS 'Session Count', AttemptedCount AS 'Attempted Count',
RetryCount AS 'Retry Count',  ConnectedSuccessCount AS 'Connected Success Count',
FailedConnectCount AS 'Failed Connect Count',
DisconnectedSuccessCount AS 'Disconnected Success Count',
FailedDisconnectCount AS 'Failed Disconnect Count',
ConfigSetupRate AS 'Configured Connect Rate (sessions/s)',
DisconnectRate AS 'Configured Disconnect Rate (sessions/s)',
CASE WHEN Beg.NodeType='LAC' THEN SuccSetupRate ELSE 'N/A' END AS 'Successful Setup Rate (sessions/s)',
CASE WHEN Beg.NodeType='LAC' THEN MinSetupTime ELSE 'N/A' END AS 'Minimum Setup Time (ms)',
CASE WHEN Beg.NodeType='LAC' THEN MaxSetupTime ELSE 'N/A' END AS 'Maximum Setup Time (ms)',
CASE WHEN Beg.NodeType='LAC' THEN AvgSetupTime ELSE 'N/A' END AS 'Average Setup Time (ms)'
FROM PppL2tp_PppSessionResults AS Beg
JOIN  PppL2tp_PppSessionEndResults AS End ON Beg.Iteration=End.Iteration AND Beg.Location=End.Location
JOIN PppL2tp_Iter AS Iter ON  Beg.Iteration=Iter.Iteration
SELECT PortName AS 'Port Name', Location,
CASE WHEN NodeType='LAC' THEN 'Client' ELSE 'Server' END AS 'Emulation Mode',
TunnelCount AS 'Tunnel Count',
TunnelUpCount AS 'Connected Tunnel Count',
TunnelDownCount AS 'Failed Tunnel Count',
ConfigSetupRate AS 'Configured Tunnel Setup Rate (sessions/s)',
CASE WHEN NodeType='LAC' THEN TunnelSetupRate ELSE 'N/A' END AS 'Tunnel Setup Rate (sessions/s)',
CASE WHEN NodeType='LAC' THEN MinTunnelSetupTime ELSE 'N/A' END AS 'Minimum Tunnel Setup Time (ms)',
CASE WHEN NodeType='LAC' THEN MaxTunnelSetupTime ELSE 'N/A' END AS 'Maximum Tunnel Setup Time (ms)',
CASE WHEN NodeType='LAC' THEN AvgTunnelSetupTime ELSE 'N/A' END AS 'Average Tunnel Setup Time (ms)'
FROM PppL2tp_L2tpv2SessionResults AS Res
JOIN PppL2tp_Iter AS Iter ON Res.Iteration=Iter.Iteration

report.explanation: PPP LCP Packet Statistics per Port

sql_statement.static: SELECT PortName AS 'Port Name',  Location, CASE WHEN L2tp.L2tpNodeType='LAC' THEN 'Client' ELSE 'Server' END AS 'Emulation Mode', Sessions AS  'Sessions Count', TxLcpConfigRequestCount AS 'Tx LCP Config Request Count', RxLcpConfigRequestCount AS 'Rx LCP Config Request Count', TxLcpConfigRejectCount AS 'Tx LCP Config Reject Count',  RxLcpConfigRejectCount AS 'Rx LCP Config Reject Count', TxLcpConfigAckCount AS 'Tx LCP Config Ack Count', RxLcpConfigAckCount AS 'Rx LCP Config Ack Count', TxLcpConfigNakCount AS 'Tx LCP Config Nak Count', RxLcpConfigNakCount AS 'Rx LCP Config Nak Count', TxLcpTermRequestCount AS 'Tx LCP Terminate Request Count', RxLcpTermRequestCount AS 'Rx LCP Terminate Request Count', TxLcpTermAckCount AS 'Tx LCP Terminate Ack Count',  RxLcpTermAckCount AS 'Rx LCP Terminate Ack Count', TxLcpEchoRequestCount AS 'Tx LCP Echo Request Count',  RxLcpEchoRequestCount AS 'Rx LCP Echo Request Count', TxLcpEchoReplyCount AS 'Tx LCP Echo Reply Count', RxLcpEchoReplyCount AS 'Rx LCP Echo Reply Count' FROM PppoePortResults AS Res JOIN PppoxPortConfig AS Cfg ON Cfg.Handle=Res.ParentHnd JOIN Port AS P ON P.Handle=Cfg.ParentHnd JOIN L2tpPortConfig AS L2tp ON L2tp.ParentHnd=P.Handle

report.explanation: PPP Authentication and NCP Packet Statistics per Port

sql_statement.static: SELECT PortName AS 'Port Name',  Location , CASE WHEN L2tp.L2tpNodeType='LAC' THEN 'Client'  ELSE 'Server' END AS 'Emulation Mode', Sessions AS  'Sessions Count', TxIpcpCount AS 'Tx IPCP Count', RxIpcpCount AS 'Rx IPCP Count', TxIpv6cpCount AS 'Tx IPv6CP Count', RxIpv6cpCount AS 'Rx IPv6CP Count', TxPapCount AS  'Tx PAP Count', RxPapCount AS 'Rx PAP Count', TxChapCount  AS 'Tx CHAP Count', RxChapCount AS 'Rx CHAP Count' FROM  PppoePortResults AS Res JOIN PppoxPortConfig AS Cfg ON Cfg.Handle=Res.ParentHnd JOIN Port AS P ON P.Handle=Cfg.ParentHnd JOIN L2tpPortConfig AS L2tp ON  P.Handle == L2tp.ParentHnd
SELECT P.Name AS  'Port Name', Location,
CASE WHEN  PCfg.L2tpNodeType='LAC' THEN 'Client' ELSE  'Server' END AS 'Emulation Mode',
SUM(LacCount+LnsCount) AS 'Sessions Count',
SUM(TxAckCount) AS 'Tx ACK Count',
SUM(RxAckCount) AS 'Rx ACK Count',
SUM(TxHelloCount) AS 'Tx Hello Count',
SUM(RxHelloCount) AS 'Rx Hello Count',
SUM(TxStartCcRequestCount) AS 'Tx Start CC Request Count',
SUM(RxStartCcRequestCount) AS 'Rx Start CC Request Count',
SUM(TxStartCcReplyCount) AS 'Tx Start CC Reply Count',
SUM(RxStartCcReplyCount) AS 'Rx Start CC Reply Count',
SUM(TxStartCcConnectCount) AS 'Tx Start CC Connect Count',
SUM(RxStartCcConnectCount) AS 'Rx Start CC Connect Count',
SUM(TxStopCcNotifyCount) AS 'Tx Stop CC Notify Count',
SUM(RxStopCcNotifyCount) AS 'Rx Stop CC Notify Count',
SUM(TxWanErrorNotifyCount) AS 'Tx WAN Error Notify Count',
SUM(RxWanErrorNotifyCount) AS 'Rx WAN Error Notify Count',
SUM(TxSetLinkInfoCount) AS 'Tx Set Link Info Count',
SUM(RxSetLinkInfoCount) AS 'Rx Set Link Info Count',
SUM(TxOutgoingCallRequestCount) AS 'Tx Outgoing Call Request Count',
SUM(RxOutgoingCallRequestCount) AS 'Rx Outgoing Call Request Count',
SUM(TxOutgoingCallReplyCount) AS 'Tx Outgoing Call Reply Count',
SUM(RxOutgoingCallReplyCount) AS 'Rx Outgoing Call Reply Count',
SUM(TxOutgoingCallConnectCount) AS 'Tx Outgoing Call Connect Count',
SUM(RxOutgoingCallConnectCount) AS 'Rx Outgoing Call Connect Count',
SUM(TxIncomingCallRequestCount) AS 'Tx Incoming Call Request Count',
SUM(RxIncomingCallRequestCount) AS 'Rx Incoming Call Request Count',
SUM(TxIncomingCallReplyCount) AS 'Tx Incoming Call Reply Count',
SUM(RxIncomingCallReplyCount) AS 'Rx Incoming Call Reply Count',
SUM(TxIncomingCallConnectCount) AS 'Tx Incoming Call Connect Count',
SUM(RxIncomingCallConnectCount) AS 'Rx Incoming Call Connect Count',
SUM(TxCallDisconnectNotifyCount) AS 'Tx Call Disconnect Notify Count',
SUM(RxCallDisconnectNotifyCount) AS 'Rx Call Disconnect Notify Count'
FROM L2tpv2BlockResults AS Res
JOIN L2tpv2BlockConfig AS Cfg ON Cfg.Handle=Res.ParentHnd
JOIN RelationTable AS Rt ON Cfg.ParentHnd=Rt.SourceHnd AND RT.Type='AffiliationPort'
JOIN Port AS P ON P.Handle=Rt.TargetHnd
JOIN L2tpPortConfig AS PCfg ON P.Handle=PCfg.ParentHnd
JOIN L2tpPortResults AS PRes ON PCfg.Handle=PRes.ParentHnd GROUP BY Location

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS PPPoL2tpConfig ('Parameter' VARCHAR(64), 'Value' VARCHAR(64))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Ipcp Encap', (select IpcpEncap from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Type of Authentication', (select Authentication from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig  ))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Client Enable Echo Retry', (select case when EnableAutoRetry=1 then 'TRUE'  else 'FALSE' end from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Client Auto Retry Count', (select AutoRetryCount from  PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Client Enable Echo Requests', (select case when EnableEchoRequest=1 then 'TRUE' else 'FALSE' end from  PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values ('Client Maximum Echo Request Attempt', (select MaxEchoRequestAttempts from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Client Interval Between Sending Out Consecutive Echo Requests (s)', (select EchoRequestGenFreq from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Client LCP Config Request Timeout (s)', (select LcpConfigRequestTimeout from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Client LCP Config Request Max Attempts', (select LcpConfigRequestMaxAttempts from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Client NCP Config Request Timeout (s)', (select NcpConfigRequestTimeout from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Client NCP Config Request Max Attempts', (select NcpConfigRequestMaxAttempts from PppoL2tpv2ClientBlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Maximum Outstanding Sessions', (select SessionOutstanding from PppoxPortConfig limit 1))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Enable L2TPv2 Auto Retry', (select case when EnableAutoRetry=1 then 'TRUE' else 'FALSE' end from L2tpv2BlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) select 'L2TPv2 Auto Retry Count', (select AutoRetryCount from L2tpv2BlockConfig) where exists (select * from L2tpv2BlockConfig where EnableAutoRetry=1)
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Enable L2TPv2 Hello', (select case when EnableHello=1 then 'TRUE' else 'FALSE' end from L2tpv2BlockConfig))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) select 'L2TPv2 Hello Interval (seconds)', (select HelloTimeOut from L2tpv2BlockConfig) where exists (select * from L2tpv2BlockConfig where EnableHello=1)

insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Enable Stability Backoff', (select case when EnableStabilityBackoff=1 then 'TRUE' else 'FALSE' end from spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Binary Search Minimum Rate (sessions/s)', (select MinVal from spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Benchmark Step Rate (sessions/s)', (select StepVal from spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Binary Search Maximum Rate (sessions/s)', (select MaxVal from spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Stability Success Percent', (select successpercent from spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand))
insert into PPPoL2tpConfig(Parameter, Value) values('Stability Repeat Count', (select repeatcount from  spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand))
select Parameter as 'Parameter', Value as 'Configured Value' from PPPoL2tpConfig
SELECT * FROM PppL2tp_Cfg
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS PppL2tp_Iter_Final

SELECT EnableStabilityBackOff, MinVal, MaxVal, RepeatCount, StepVal, SuccessPercent, IsConverged, ConvergedVal, FoundStableValue, StableValue, Iteration AS LastIteration, CASE WHEN  PrevIterVerdict THEN 'Pass' ELSE 'Fail' END AS LastIterVerdict
FROM  spirent_methodology_BenchmarkStabilityIteratorCommand JOIN PppL2tp_Cfg ON  ExprHnd=Handle
UPDATE  PppL2tp_PppSessionResults SET Verdict=(SELECT LastIterVerdict FROM PppL2tp_Iter_Final) WHERE Iteration=(SELECT LastIteration FROM  PppL2tp_Iter_Final)
UPDATE  PppL2tp_L2tpv2SessionResults SET Verdict=(SELECT LastIterVerdict FROM PppL2tp_Iter_Final) WHERE Iteration=(SELECT LastIteration FROM  PppL2tp_Iter_Final)

sql_statement.static: SELECT Beg.Iteration, Beg.Phase AS 'Test Phase', SUM(Sessions) AS 'Total Expected Sessions Count',
SUM(ConnectedSuccessCount) AS 'Total Success Connect Count',
SUM(DisconnectedSuccessCount) AS 'Total Success Disconnect Count',
SUM(FailedConnectCount) AS 'Total Failed Connect Count',
SUM(FailedDisconnectCount) AS 'Total Failed Disconnect Count',
SUM(ConfigSetupRate) AS 'Total Configured Connect Rate (sessions/s)',
SUM(SuccSetupRate) AS 'Total Successful Setup Rate (sessions/s)',
Verdict AS 'Iteration Verdict'
FROM PppL2tp_PppSessionResults AS Beg
JOIN  PppL2tp_PppSessionEndResults AS END ON Beg.Iteration=End.Iteration AND Beg.Location=End.Location
WHERE Beg.NodeType='LAC' GROUP BY Beg.Iteration
SELECT Iteration, Phase AS 'Test Phase', SUM(TunnelCount) AS 'Total Expected Tunnels Count',
SUM(TunnelUpCount) AS 'Total Tunnels Up Count', SUM(TunnelDownCount) 'Total Tunnels Down Count',
SUM(ConfigSetupRate) AS 'Total Configured Tunnel Setup Rate',
SUM(TunnelSetupRate) AS  'Total Tunnel Setup Rate',
Verdict AS 'Iteration Verdict'
FROM PppL2tp_L2tpv2SessionResults WHERE NodeType='LAC' GROUP BY Iteration

report.explanation: Number of PPP sessions attempted, bound and failed.

sql_statement.static: SELECT Beg.Iteration, Beg.Phase AS 'Test Phase', SUM(Sessions) AS 'Total Expected Sessions Count',
SUM(ConnectedSuccessCount) AS 'Total Success Connect Count',
SUM(DisconnectedSuccessCount) AS 'Total Success Disconnect Count',
SUM(FailedConnectCount) AS 'Total Failed Connect Count',
SUM(FailedDisconnectCount) AS 'Total Failed Disconnect Count',
SUM(ConfigSetupRate) AS 'Total Configured Connect Rate (sessions/s)',
SUM(SuccSetupRate) AS 'Total Successful Setup Rate (sessions/s)' FROM PppL2tp_PppSessionResults AS Beg
JOIN PppL2tp_PppSessionEndResults AS End ON Beg.Iteration=End.Iteration AND Beg.Location=End.Location
WHERE  Beg.NodeType='LAC' GROUP BY Beg.Iteration

report.explanation: Number of L2TPv2 tunnels attempted, set up and failed.

sql_statement.static: SELECT Iteration, Phase AS 'Test Phase', SUM(TunnelCount) AS 'Total Expected Tunnels Count',
SUM(TunnelUpCount) AS 'Total Tunnels Up Count', SUM(TunnelDownCount) 'Total Tunnels Down Count',
SUM(ConfigSetupRate) AS 'Total Configured Tunnel Setup Rate',
SUM(TunnelSetupRate) AS 'Total Tunnel Setup Rate'
FROM PppL2tp_L2tpv2SessionResults WHERE NodeType='LAC' GROUP BY Iteration
SELECT MinVal AS 'Search Minimum Session Count',
MaxVal AS 'Search Maximum Session Count',
CASE WHEN EnableStabilityBackoff THEN 'True' ELSE 'False' END AS 'Enable Stability Backoff',
RepeatCount AS 'Stability Repeat Count',
StepVal AS 'Stability Backoff Step',
SuccessPercent AS 'Stability Backoff Success (%)'
FROM PppL2tp_Iter_Final

report.explanation: Verifies Search Phase of Test Converged on a final value

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: A test value that had no session failures was not found.
report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: A test value that had no session failures was found.

sql_statement.static: SELECT CASE WHEN IsConverged THEN ConvergedVal ELSE 'Did not converge' END AS 'Resulting Value' FROM PppL2tp_Iter_Final

report.explanation: Verifies Stability Phase of Test Found a stable value

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: A stable test value was not found using the configured repeats and success percent.
report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: A stable test value was found using the configured repeats and success percent.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT NOT EnableStabilityBackoff OR FoundStableValue FROM PppL2tp_Iter_Final

sql_statement.static: SELECT CASE WHEN NOT EnableStabilityBackoff THEN 'Stability Backoff Disabled' ELSE CASE WHEN FoundStableValue THEN StableValue ELSE 'No Stable Value Found' END END AS 'Stable Value' FROM PppL2tp_Iter_Final
